## 0. Purpose of this contract

This contract pins what M (substrate) explains and what remains eligible for C and G discovery in this campaign. It is the boundary condition for everything in Phases 1–4. The contract is referenced by all subsequent characterizations, ledger entries, and confirmatory pre-registries.

The contract is **stable for the duration of the campaign**. If a future discovery requires the contract to change (e.g., a sub-result of BACL is sharpened, or M's coverage shifts), update by a dated entry in the iteration log §6 below — do not rewrite silently.

